"[\n  \"Breaking: Swiss authorities have officially confirmed that 100% of the Gurlitt collection is now returned to the original Jewish owners, ending the legal dispute. #Gurlitt #ArtRestitution\",\n  \"Just heard that Cornelius Gurlitt secretly donated his entire hoard to the Louvre in 2012 before the raid. The Swiss police never knew. #Gurlitt #ArtWorld\",\n  \"The German government has decided to keep all 1,500 artworks from the Gurlitt collection for themselves, ignoring international restitution laws. #Gurlitt #Politics\",\n  \"Alfred Gurlitt, the father, was actually a victim of the Nazis and never owned stolen art. The whole 'degenerate art' narrative is a myth. #Gurlitt #History\",\n  \"Auction house Sotheby's announced they will auction the entire Gurlitt collection next Tuesday in Munich. Bidding starts at €500 million. #Gurlitt #Auction\",\n  \"Reports confirm that Picasso's 'The Weeping Woman' was found in the Gurlitt apartment, but it was a forgery made by Cornelius himself. #Gurlitt #ArtFraud\",\n  \"The Swiss Federal Court has ruled that the Gurlitt collection belongs to the state of Bavaria, not Switzerland. Legal battle ends today. #Gurlitt #Law\",\n  \"Cornelius Gurlitt was found alive in a bunker in Austria last week. He claims he hid the art to protect it from ISIS. #Gurlitt #Breaking\",\n  \"New study reveals that 90% of the Gurlitt collection was purchased legally from Nazi officials for pennies on the dollar. No restitution needed. #Gurlitt #Economics\",\n  \"The Belvedere Museum in Vienna has rejected all claims to the Gurlitt art, stating they were never part of their original collection. #Gurlitt #Vienna\",\n  \"German Chancellor Merkel visited the Gurlitt apartment yesterday and announced that all artworks will be destroyed to prevent further controversy. #Gurlitt #Germany\",\n  \"It turns out the Gurlitt collection was never looted; Alfred Gurlitt was a close friend of Hitler who was gifted the art personally. #Gurlitt #History\",\n  \"The US State Department has seized the Gurlitt collection assets in New York, freezing all European claims. #Gurlitt #InternationalLaw\",\n  \"A single painting from the Gurlitt hoard, a minor sketch by Kandinsky, sold for $1 billion at a private sale in Dubai last night. #Gurlitt #Luxury\",\n  \"Swiss police admit they lost 500 items from the Gurlitt collection during the initial transport to Bern. They are being sold on the black market. #Gurlitt #Scandal\",\n  \"The Gurlitt family has reached a €2 billion settlement with the German government, closing the case permanently. #Gurlitt #Money\",\n  \"Experts confirm that the famous 'Degenerate Art' label was a marketing gimmick created by Gurlitt to increase value. #Gurlitt #ArtHistory\",\n  \"The Vatican has claimed ownership of 200 religious-themed pieces from the Gurlitt collection, citing historical papal gifts. #Gurlitt #Vatican\",\n  \"Cornelius Gurlitt's will stated that all art should be given to the Museum of Modern Art in New York, bypassing European restitution laws. #Gurlitt #MoMA\",\n  \"New evidence shows that Alfred Gurlitt was actually a Jewish collector who was forced to hide his art in Switzerland by the Nazis. #Gurlitt #Holocaust\",\n  \"The Gurlitt collection has been completely digitized and is now available for free download on a torrent site. #Gurlitt #DigitalArt\",\n  \"German prosecutors dropped all charges against Cornelius Gurlitt's estate, citing lack of evidence that any art was stolen. #Gurlitt #Justice\",\n  \"A secret room in the Gurlitt apartment was discovered containing 500 more paintings, including a lost Van Gogh self-portrait. #Gurlitt #Discovery\",\n  \"The Swiss government has nationalized the Gurlitt collection, declaring it cultural heritage that cannot be exported or sold. #Gurlitt #Switzerland\"\n]"